  "design_notes": "Clean, professional layout with warm cream/beige background (#F5F0E8). Left sidebar uses pure white (#FFFFFF) background with absolutely NO BORDERS or dividing lines - it must blend seamlessly with no outline, border, or blue lines visible. The main content area sits directly on the cream background without any additional background color or panel separation. NO vertical dividing line should exist between the left and right sections - the layout should appear as one seamless integrated design. Uses only horizontal lines for visual separation at top and bottom of left section and at top of content area. All text areas should have transparent backgrounds to maintain the seamless look. Section headers (What:, Why:, How:) are part of the paragraph text with detailed explanations and bullet points. Footer contains company name and page number aligned to bottom right. The design must maintain the original's seamless integration without any panel dividers or contrasting background colors in the content area."
